      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNLIT AMBER (6) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at Q Lakeside but was a Restricted WIN winner two back at this track. Can turn form around here. BUNDY ALL GO (1) has been in super consistent form, last time breaking from this same box when second in a Restricted WIN at this track (19.96) and making it three straight placings. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Can measure up. ONLY EASY (3) finished well back at Q Lakeside last time when a 8 length eighth (22.57) but scored five back at Rockhampton (23.89). Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to give a good account. MOCKERY MIRAGE (7) has won at this course and distance – sure to figure prominently.",
